Imagery Description: Woman with phiale of eggs and fillet in r. and mirror and fillet in 1., running to 1. and looking to r.
Additional Notes: Found with 48460Non Sepcified2 (below), 48455 (no. 11), an early squat lekythos by the Thyrsus Painter (48464) and a lebes gamikos in applied red (48457 = App. I. no. 126, pi. 238e). The plant to the r. of woman should be compared with those on nos. 11, 106, 109.
